Maya Lin has been commissioned by the Nisei-American Veteran's Electronic Library to design the Nisei monument in Gardena California.<br><br>
Or at least we would like to commission Maya for this task.<br><br>
Information on how you can contribute monetraily to this work is available from us at the mailing address below.<br><br>
I went to High School with Maya's brother Hideo and remember how she would follow behind us when we went fishing.<br><br>
The prettiest Japanese-American ever created by the God Youshi!!<br><br>
Peace<br><br>
